dat <- read.csv2(file = "CDA_all_2021_v2.txt", sep="\t")
#dependant variable: CDA.SCR
#independant variable: EmoId, ExpId

#transforming variables
dat$ExpId <- as.factor(dat$ExpId)
dat$EmoId <- as.factor(dat$EmoId)
dat$Participant <- as.factor(dat$Participant)
dat$ParticipantId <- as.factor(dat$ParticipantId)
dat$Sex <- as.factor(dat$Sex)
dat$Language <- as.factor(dat$Language)
dat$OverUnder <- as.factor(dat$OverUnder)
dat$CDA.Latency <- as.numeric(as.character(dat$CDA.Latency))
## Warning: NAs introduced by coercion
dat$CDA.AmpSum <- as.numeric(dat$CDA.AmpSum)
dat$CDA.SCR <- as.numeric(dat$CDA.SCR)
dat$CDA.PhasicMax <- as.numeric(dat$CDA.PhasicMax)
dat$Tonic <-  as.numeric(dat$CDA.Tonic)

#putting Ov 1 and 2, un 1 and un2 together
dat$ExpId <- as.character(dat$ExpId)
dat$ExpId <- gsub("Ov1", "o", dat$ExpId)
dat$ExpId <- gsub("Ov2", "o", dat$ExpId)
dat$ExpId <- gsub("Un1", "u", dat$ExpId)
dat$ExpId <- gsub("Un2", "u", dat$ExpId)
dat$ExpId <- as.factor(dat$ExpId)

#considering only participants with ee as their language
#dat <- dat[dat$Language=="ee",]
